                    oc:sectionTitle "Appendix: Component Icons" ],
                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasContent [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                            oc:textContent "After delivery, be ready to iterate:" ],
                        [ a oc:Table ;
                            oc:blockType "table" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 2 ;
                            oc:rowCount 7 ;
                            oc:tableCaption "After delivery, be ready to iterate" ;
                            oc:tableMarkdown """| User Request | Action |
|--------------|--------|
| "Change the colors" | Regenerate with new palette, keep content |
| "Add a section on X" | Insert new section, maintain flow |
| "Make it shorter" | Condense, prioritize key points |
| "The flow is wrong" | Rebuild architecture based on correction |
| "Use our brand instead" | Switch from prospect brand to seller brand |
| "Add more detail on step 3" | Expand that section specifically |
| "Can I get this as a PDF?" | Provide print-optimized version |
""" ],
                        [ a oc:Paragraph ;
                            oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                            oc:contentOrder 3 ;
                            oc:textContent "**Remember**: Default to prospect's brand colors, but seller can adjust to their own brand or a neutral palette after initial build." ] ;
                    oc:sectionLevel 2 ;
                    oc:sectionOrder 54 ;
                    oc:sectionTitle "Phase 7: Iteration Support" ],
                [ a oc:Section ;
                    oc:hasSubsection [ a oc:Section ;
                            oc:hasContent [ a oc:CodeExample ;
                                    oc:blockType "code_block" ;
                                    oc:codeContent """.arrow {
    stroke: var(--text-muted);
    stroke-width: 2;
    fill: none;
    marker-end: url(#arrowhead);
}

.arrow.active {
    stroke: var(--accent);
    stroke-dasharray: 8 4;
    animation: flowDash 1s linear infinite;
}
""" ;
                                    oc:codeLanguage "css" ;
